{{Quote|Tonight we gather here in the shadows of our sacred Soul Trees to honor these young Ewoks.|Chirpa|<ref name="Trees" />}}
The '''Festival of Hoods''' was an [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] ceremony that happened when a [[Wokling/Legends|wokling]] came of age. This festival marked the transition from wokling to Ewok. Ewoks would be given their hoods.<ref name="Trees" />

